name: Optical Nerve Rorschach
description: The back of your eyelids burn, the flickering image warping- no- wiggling up the screen. A tension starts to build in your head starting from the occipital and frontal lobe. A squeezing, pressing pressure threatening to build like a tsunami. First pulling at the edges of your mind- before crashing down with destructive, flooding force. Blackness follows, but you can still see the tv flickering.
